# ==============================================================================
# ðŸ™ˆ File: .gitignore
# Version: 0.5.0 (Data Science Release)
# Description: Defines build artifacts and data exclusions for the repository.
# ==============================================================================

# --- 1. Python & System Artifacts ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.DS_Store
venv/
.pytest_cache/

# --- 2. Secrets & Ansible ---
# CRITICAL: Never commit passwords or keys
.vault_pass
.env
*.retry
infra/ansible/inventory/host_vars/secret_*.yml

# --- 3. Research Data (Excluded) ---
# Raw logs are too big for Git. We track the 'docs/showcase' summaries instead.
research_data/
data/
storage_history.csv

# --- 4. Analysis & Reports ---
# Ignore intermediate working files...
analysis/*

# ... BUT explicitly track these valuable summary reports:
!analysis/daily_reports/
!analysis/archive/
!analysis/**/*.md

# --- 5. Documentation & Showcase ---
# Ensure our academic proofs are always tracked
!docs/showcase/

# --- 6. Infrastructure Volumes ---
infra/database/data/
mosquitto/data/
mosquitto/log/
influxdb/
opensearch/

# --- 7. Large Binaries & Models ---
*.pt
*.onnx
*.tflite
*.tar.gz
*.zip
